urls.description: In honor of the holiday season and our festive new aircraft, we’re donating 1 million miles to our CARE Miles program! This program offers Mileage Plan™ members a unique and meaningful way to suppo…

data.text: We’re kicking off the holidays the best way we know how: with a new special-edition aircraft!
